<div class="about-page-container">
  <h1 class="about-title" data-i18n="about_page_title">About UnivDown</h1>
  <p class="about-intro" data-i18n="about_intro_text">
    Welcome to UnivDown! We're passionate about providing a simple, fast, and reliable way for you to download and enjoy media content from your favorite platforms, offline and on your terms.
  </p>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2 class="about-subtitle" data-i18n="about_mission_title">Our Mission</h2>
    <p data-i18n="about_mission_text_1">
      In a world overflowing with online content, we believe accessing media you love shouldn't be complicated. Our mission is to offer a straightforward, user-friendly tool that empowers you to save videos, audios, and images easily.
    </p>
    <p data-i18n="about_mission_text_2">
      Whether it's for offline viewing during commutes, educational purposes, creative remixing, or simply keeping a personal archive, UnivDown aims to be your go-to solution, always focusing on simplicity and respecting user rights and platform terms.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2 class="about-subtitle" data-i18n="about_what_we_offer_title">What We Offer</h2>
     <p data-i18n="about_offer_intro">
       UnivDown is designed with you in mind, focusing on core features that enhance your downloading experience:
     </p>
    <ul class="features-list">
      <li data-i18n="about_feature_simple"><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> <strong>Simplicity First:</strong> A clean, intuitive interface. Paste a link, choose your quality, and download. It's that easy.</li>
      <li data-i18n="about_feature_platforms"><i class="ri-vidicon-line"></i> <strong>Multiple Platforms:</strong> Currently supporting downloads from major platforms like YouTube, TikTok, Instagram, and Erome, with plans to expand.</li>
      <li data-i18n="about_feature_quality"><i class="ri-hd-line"></i> <strong>Quality Choices:</strong> Download videos and audio in the best available qualities, including HD options where applicable.</li>
      <li data-i18n="about_feature_nomark"><i class="ri-water-flash-line"></i> <strong>No Watermarks (TikTok):</strong> Get your favorite TikTok videos clean and ready to share or reuse (respecting original creator rights).</li>
      <li data-i18n="about_feature_speed"><i class="ri-speed-up-line"></i> <strong>Fast & Reliable:</strong> We strive to process links quickly and provide stable download connections.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2 class="about-subtitle" data-i18n="about_our_values_title">Our Commitment</h2>
     <ul class="values-list">
        <li data-i18n="about_value_ux">
           <strong>User Experience:</strong> We prioritize a smooth, ad-minimal experience. Your time and focus matter.
        </li>
        <li data-i18n="about_value_legal">
           <strong>Responsible Use:</strong> We encourage users to respect copyright laws and the terms of service of the platforms they download from. UnivDown is intended for personal and fair use. Please check our <a href="/terms-use" data-i18n="[link]link_terms">Terms of Use</a> and <a href="/disclaimer" data-i18n="[link]link_disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>.
        </li>
         <li data-i18n="about_value_dev">
           <strong>Continuous Improvement:</strong> We are actively developing UnivDown, listening to feedback, fixing bugs, and working to support more content types and platforms.
         </li>
     </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Opcional: Llamada a la acción o contacto -->
  <section class="about-section connect-section">
    <h2 class="about-subtitle" data-i18n="about_connect_title">Connect With Us</h2>
    <p data-i18n="about_connect_text">
      Have suggestions, questions, or encountered an issue? We'd love to hear from you! Visit our <a href="/contact" data-i18n="[link]link_contact">Contact page</a> or follow us on our social channels (see footer).
    </p>
  </section>

